<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Abjure" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Abjure,</orth> 1) to renounce upon oath: <cit><quote>this rough magic I here a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. V, 51</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.1.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 1, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 2, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 2.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 4, 211</bibl>.<lb />2) to recant upon oath: <cit><quote>I here a. the taints and blames I laid upon myself.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.123" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 123</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>